{"tid":358453,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個人生遺憾","createTime":"2017-08-13T17:27:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T22:01:46.000Z","uid":135967,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c913ab7faad4390fce2ab03f55aa97020505b707","tid":358453,"uid":135967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T17:27:32.000Z","msg":"細細個放暑假 因為老豆老母要翻工<br />\n所以住係外地既公公就會翻黎照顧我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對住佢既日子唔長 每年正係得一個月左右<br />\n個陣我好細個 又唔生性又成日唔爹唔吊咁成日都激親佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以佢就逼我學煮野 整下d菜色  訓練下耐性咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （佢退休前係個中廚）<br />\n但個陣因為懶 樣樣都學得一半 整到勁難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有一年佢臨飛個晚 仲話下年翻黎希望我煮到一餐好味既晚餐比佢食<br />\n我仲拍曬心口講好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出年一定令你滿意<br />\n點知佢一飛翻去 過左2個月就心臟病發 走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好想煮一餐比你食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好想你好似以前咁笑笑口露出隻金牙串我有進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可惜永遠都唔會再有呢個機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5a55b5705bc9d778c60d2a5ca82c87af7a9fb1","tid":358453,"uid":68258,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T17:40:13.000Z","msg":"錯過一個好鐘意嘅人"},{"pid":"1d09d6379402d500a654f4aee858755cdd4a8b18","tid":358453,"uid":133684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T18:02:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>錯過一個好鐘意嘅人</blockquote><br />\n錯過幾次一個好鐘意嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467d091af6d5cc81bf3f2447da92f97ef40718e5","tid":358453,"uid":42422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T18:04:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>錯過一個好鐘意嘅人</blockquote><br />\n錯過幾次一個好鐘意嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSame here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a5aff0a32feddea00a752cd2d42db72f1cfe68","tid":358453,"uid":136225,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T18:06:15.000Z","msg":"明明決心唔想激嬲啊媽 但次次都用唔好嘅態度同佢講野"},{"pid":"9409a126f6cda2a659b12fd3d5744ee693eac56e","tid":358453,"uid":133684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T18:14:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>錯過一個好鐘意嘅人</blockquote><br />\n錯過幾次一個好鐘意嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSame here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為太鐘意一個人，好怕有日會失去佢，一路拖，最後錯過了時機"},{"pid":"13fb3fb30caa8695960908edb7f1b66c29205bbd","tid":358453,"uid":42422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T18:20:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>錯過一個好鐘意嘅人</blockquote><br />\n錯過幾次一個好鐘意嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSame here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為太鐘意一個人，好怕有日會失去佢，一路拖，最後錯過了時機</blockquote><br />\n我就自卑得制，唔敢面對佢，卒之佢響我生命消失得無影無蹤之後<br />\n比我發現佢原來一直都對我有意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22fd2cf0bb0310602f283330954c7539012dfad7","tid":358453,"uid":131741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T18:25:21.000Z","msg":"樓主嗰個睇到我眼濕濕<br />\n諗起細個成日覺得公公好煩好嘈 次次見到發佢脾氣<br />\n其實佢就係關心緊我 不停叫我食多啲嘢着多件衫問我想去邊度<br />\n佢走嗰陣我七歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得自己對佢冇乜感情 因為唔係公公湊大<br />\n到佢真係臨走嗰陣 對手腫晒瞓係醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喺7個孫入面專登叫我拖住佢<br />\n叫我要生性 話我知佢係好錫我嘅<br />\n<br />\n到而家大個喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我連佢個樣都記唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e591228003e6f252d3137fd2ee4c94986ac278a","tid":358453,"uid":135967,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:19:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主嗰個睇到我眼濕濕<br />\n諗起細個成日覺得公公好煩好嘈 次次見到發佢脾氣<br />\n其實佢就係關心緊我 不停叫我食多啲嘢着多件衫問我想去邊度<br />\n佢走嗰陣我七歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得自己對佢冇乜感情 因為唔係公公湊大<br />\n到佢真係臨走嗰陣 對手腫晒瞓係醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喺7個孫入面專登叫我拖住佢<br />\n叫我要生性 話我知佢係好錫我嘅<br />\n<br />\n到而家大個喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我連佢個樣都記唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屋企人既愛一直都喺我地身邊 只不過喺我地太習以為常 冇察覺到姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打要珍惜眼前人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bfeecb2255b2eee25f203aa4a51ca130dbc42dc","tid":358453,"uid":135967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:21:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>錯過一個好鐘意嘅人</blockquote><br />\n錯過幾次一個好鐘意嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSame here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為太鐘意一個人，好怕有日會失去佢，一路拖，最後錯過了時機</blockquote><br />\n我就自卑得制，唔敢面對佢，卒之佢響我生命消失得無影無蹤之後<br />\n比我發現佢原來一直都對我有意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n經一事長一智<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記住把握將來既機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"122bb6faa5b7edd60018ce918e25775a0923e754","tid":358453,"uid":112622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:24:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c451aa766606470b6d5ebaba82a7c093f84f4e53","tid":358453,"uid":96704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:54:25.000Z","msg":"唔只一個，有好撚多個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32fcf71a8a5d02afd15d28a362b3bf9f79b229a8","tid":358453,"uid":114159,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T09:04:34.000Z","msg":"未試過響中學時期同學生妹發生初戀, 之後再害害羞羞咁互相獻出第一次, 真係一個永不磨滅既人生遺憾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"032add947169a32d1e976384b9da56034d1309f9","tid":358453,"uid":26624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T09:10:33.000Z","msg":"好後悔細個嘅時候因爲小問題而同個女仔分手，遺憾嘅係明明大家都好鐘意對方，即使分開左咁耐到而家仍然會聯絡，但無奈嘅係所有野同當初都唔同晒，亦再冇可能一齊返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f201384031ba859f38911d5c8c762dd072c8ccb","tid":358453,"uid":114735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T09:10:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f96d412f39abec331b7492b9f4f0c166e87ca69a","tid":358453,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T09:32:55.000Z","msg":"做一個孝順仔"},{"pid":"370310273ccc2774d9cc9616c7a0a18fd4cb3f29","tid":358453,"uid":28515,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T09:35:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">愛情根本無資格做人生遺憾</span>"},{"pid":"02bda34d65c2ce2c7d507427c042c5aa4e35aaa8","tid":358453,"uid":12360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:02:29.000Z","msg":"中三揀錯科"},{"pid":"d462a77e38275f86082b6a0f5e994355738bd948","tid":358453,"uid":35365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:06:23.000Z","msg":"為咗食個早餐搞到interview遲咗幾分鐘<br />\n雖然唔知係咪真係關事<br />\n但我硬係覺得就係呢件事令到冇咗個offer"},{"pid":"9395fb6ccfb17edadbc90e7a15eef3eacd7f5b6b","tid":358453,"uid":135967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:53:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好後悔細個嘅時候因爲小問題而同個女仔分手，遺憾嘅係明明大家都好鐘意對方，即使分開左咁耐到而家仍然會聯絡，但無奈嘅係所有野同當初都唔同晒，亦再冇可能一齊返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有d野唔喺你以為就冇可能ga 我相信只要你肯試  就仲有機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你差個決心同勇氣炸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲中意人就去馬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28484dcc9f22e1c626d5bd8f5a2746db74f21f40","tid":358453,"uid":135967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:56:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔只一個，有好撚多個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你宜家最大遺憾喺咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd021f07bc3d3ceb76fd22f6c1f4b9ab86dfe0c","tid":358453,"uid":136424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:04:39.000Z","msg":"最大遺憾係自己太天真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以比男人呃"},{"pid":"63aa1a05a213373112e4b8273207448f4df052fb","tid":358453,"uid":64925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:05:40.000Z","msg":"做唔到f1賽車手"},{"pid":"3d6f949285bc304e1892d1f7c9a35cd56a9594e3","tid":358453,"uid":5422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:06:50.000Z","msg":"同爸爸講一聲多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d1248d1fa16ec29ad5760c7e7488837f194c244","tid":358453,"uid":117834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:13:44.000Z","msg":"咩都做唔到 輸比自己"}]}